reviewText: Great and very fast shipping service, My blue ray was a very good quality and one who like Indian songs this was a very good pick. you will enjoy it.

There's alot more dance music on this collection than the first one, so I guess dancing is probably the main theme for this collection.

And there's is not alot of the beautiful girls that I look forward to watching when I watch Bollywood song videos.  In many cases here, there are mostly guys dancing or acting like idiots and retards on many of the videos.

I don't think I can watch this one again any time soon.
